ğŸ” What About Authentication?
Your code doesnâ€™t include authentication. Many APIs (like Jira, Twilio, Slack, etc.) require an API key or OAuth token.

You can add:


r.setRequestHeader('Authorization', 'Bearer YOUR_API_KEY_HERE');
Or you can use ServiceNow's built-in credentials with:


r.setAuthenticationProfile(authenticationType, profileName);
âœ… When and Where to Use This
Use Case	Examples
